    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――LizNoir海外ツアー追加公演の少し前",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "あはは……ふふ……！\nもー、頑張り過ぎだよ……えぇー！",
      "startTime": 5.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　愛の声だ……誰かと話してるのか？\n随分楽しそうだが……愛しかいないな",
      "startTime": 14.3392074555,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それは食べちゃダメなやつなのでは……！\n……えっ、美味しい！？　えぇ～～！！",
      "startTime": 21.7811554335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "通話中、なのか……？　人の出入りもあるし\n少し声量を落としてもらった方がいいかもな",
      "startTime": 29.6562005691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "そっ、そんな所に身一つで飛び込むなんて……！\nあ、危なーーい！",
      "startTime": 36.4079265856,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "愛、少し声を落として……聞こえてないのか？\n愛。……あーいー！　……愛ーー！！",
      "startTime": 43.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "ひゃあっ！？　びっくりした！\nえっ、え、{user}さん！？",
      "startTime": 49.3960097631,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "すすす、すみません！\nイヤホンをしていたので気付きませんでした！",
      "startTime": 52.9960097631,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "いや、こっちも大声をあげてすまない\n一体何をしてたんだ？",
      "startTime": 58.6999997457,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "あ……実は、最近ハマっている番組がありまして\nレッスンの空き時間に、配信サイトで観ていたんです",
      "startTime": 65.1917920114,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "『世界のお祭り突撃GO！』っていう番組なんですが\n{user}さんはご存知ですか？",
      "startTime": 72.6251253447,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、確か世界各国のお祭りに芸能人が体当たりで\n参加して、いろんなことに挑戦、取材する番組だよな",
      "startTime": 79.2333366395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "はい、まさにその番組です！　毎回、番組の最後に\n海外の温泉を紹介してくれるのも楽しいんですよ",
      "startTime": 88.7548115415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "この番組に、私そっくりのモノマネ芸人さんの\n『大美山ラブ』さんがよく出演していらっしゃるんです",
      "startTime": 96.5881448748,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "それがきっかけで観始めたら、毎回ドキドキハラハラ\n涙と笑い、感動の連続で、すっかりハマっちゃいました",
      "startTime": 104.7548115415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、星見プロの事務所は実家のような安心感が\nあるので、つい気が緩んでしまって……",
      "startTime": 113.7881448748,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01-ai012.m4a",
      "text": "ヒートアップして独り言を言っちゃっていたみたいで\n……すみません、お恥ずかしいです",
      "startTime": 121.6214827857,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（BIG4になって以来、ずっと忙しいからな）\n（番組視聴がストレス解消になっているなら大目に見るか）",
      "startTime": 128.9666745504,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "今度から少し声量に気を付けてくれればいいさ\n愛が夢中になる番組、俺も観てみようかな",
      "startTime": 136.7000078838,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01-ai013.m4a",
      "text": "それなら、おすすめの回のURLをお送りしますね\n特に面白かった回トップ10があるんです！",
      "startTime": 145.0259696645,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そうなのか。どれから観ていいか分からなかったから\n助かるよ。結構なご長寿番組だったよな",
      "startTime": 151.8666684469,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01-ai014.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんですよ。実家を手伝っていた頃も\nお店でよくこの番組を流していたんです",
      "startTime": 159.4811792694,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01-ai015.m4a",
      "text": "こんなにハマったのは最近ですけど\n{user}さんも元気が出ると思います！",
      "startTime": 165.133330536,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "startTime": 168.7811823371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01-ai016.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、お疲れ様です\n……あのお話、本当ですか？",
      "startTime": 174.8478489879,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、本当だ\n今日はその件について話し合おうと思って呼んだんだ",
      "startTime": 180.1766834316,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01-ai017.m4a",
      "text": "本当に『世界のお祭り突撃GO！』から\n出演オファーが来たんですね！　やったー！",
      "startTime": 187.1889920874,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01-ai018.m4a",
      "text": "でも……なんでそんなに難しい顔をされてるんですか？\n何か問題でもあるんでしょうか？",
      "startTime": 195.6889920874,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "……喜んでいるところ、愛にはすまないけど\n俺はこの仕事を受けるのは反対だ",
      "startTime": 202.2999905905,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01-ai019.m4a",
      "text": "えぇっ！？　な、なんでですか！？\n理由を聞かせてくれないと納得出来ません",
      "startTime": 207.312849447,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "突撃取材が見所の番組だから仕方ないんだが……\n出演者が体を張り過ぎだ",
      "startTime": 214.1333239239,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "BIG4の愛が出演するのに、特番でもないし\n何より、番組の内容を考えると、怪我や病気が心配だ",
      "startTime": 220.0999905905,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01-ai020.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それは……{user}さんのご心配は\nもっともですし、絶対にないとは言えませんけど……",
      "startTime": 228.7842075989,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_01-ai021.m4a",
